{"word":"Mahalath","slug":"mahalath","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mahalath</b> <a href=\"#/H4257\">H4257</a><br/><a href=\"#/H4258\">H4258</a> <br/> 1. Called Bashemath, daughter of Ishmael<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=9'>Gen 28:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=3'>Gen 36:3</a><br/> 2. A granddaughter of David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=18'>2Ch 11:18</a><br/> 3. See <a href='S:Music'>Music</a><br/> <a href='S:Music'>Music</a>"}]}